sections.heading: to 69-22-6 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1987, ch. 234, § 84 repealed 69-22-1 to 69-22-6 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 153, §§ 148 and 150 to 152, relating to rock dust in coal mines, effective July 1, 1987. For present comparable provisions,see69-8-1 to 69-8-15 NMSA 1978.
